Release Candidate 1 Open Beta of Facial Stuff http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=818322128&tscn=1497627388 Adds new features on top of the current version, please don't subscribe to this mod if you're completely new to Facial Stuff, check out the current version instead.
